{"success":true,"result":{"Q_10109203390919-2":{"resources":[],"questions":[{"id":"Q_10109203390919-2","subjectId":101,"knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[{"id":"TM_10100000673226","main":1}],"solutionMethods":[],"resourceIds":null,"resourceIndex":0,"listenUrl":null,"listenName":null,"listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"paperIds":["P_10100126971738-2"],"books":null,"booksNew":null,"contentTypeId":1010008,"contentType2Id":0,"difficultyInt":3,"description":"阅读课外短文，回答问题","notFitMobile":0,"seconds":840,"complex":1,"nid":null,"lastEditorId":null,"finalAuditorId":null,"roughAuditorIds":null,"content":{"content":"<p style=\"text-indent: 0em; text-align: center;\"><strong>苏东坡改诗的故事</strong></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">有一次，苏东坡去王安石的书房，见桌上摆着一首只写了两句尚未写完的诗——“明月枝头叫，黄狗卧花心。”苏东坡瞧了又瞧，好生质疑，觉得明月怎能在枝头叫呢？黄狗又怎么会在花心上卧呢？于是提笔一改，将诗句改为“明月当空照，黄狗卧花荫。”</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">后来，苏东坡因为得罪了权贵，被降职调到了合浦。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">苏东坡到合浦后，一天，他外出散步，见一群小孩子围在一堆花丛前猛喊“黄狗罗罗，黑狗罗罗，快出来呀？罗罗罗，罗罗罗。 ”苏东坡走过去问小孩喊什么，小孩说，我们叫虫子快点出来。苏东坡凑近花前一看，见有几条黄色、黑色像芝麻大的小虫在花蕊里蠕动。又问小孩这是什么虫，小孩说：黄狗虫，黑狗虫。苏东坡离开花丛，来到一棵榕树下，正碰到树上一阵清脆的鸟叫声，问旁人，这是什么鸟叫？旁人答道：这叫明月鸟。苏东坡恍然大悟，自己错改了王安石的诗。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><wbr><wbr><wbr><wbr><span style=\"Line-HeiGHT: 32px; WorD-WrAp: normal; WorD-BreAK: normal\">还有一次，苏东坡去拜访王安石。看到两句未完的诗稿，认得是王丞相写的《咏菊》诗。</span>苏东坡拿起来念了一遍：西风昨夜过园林，吹落黄花满地金。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">苏东坡笑这两句诗是乱道，他认为一年四季，风各有名：春天为（　），夏天为（　），秋天为（　），冬天为（　）。这诗首句说西风，西方属金，金风行秋令也。那金风一起，梧叶飘黄，群芳零落。第二句说的黄花即菊花。此花开于深秋，最能耐久。随你老来焦干枯烂，并不落瓣。说个“吹落黄花满地金”岂不错误了？苏东坡兴之所发，依韵续诗两句：秋花不比春花落，说与诗人仔细吟。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">后来苏东坡被贬为黄州府团练副使。光阴迅速，将及一载。重九一日，天气晴朗，苏东坡去后花园看菊。走到菊花架下，只见满地铺金，枝上全无一朵。惊得目瞪口呆，半晌无语。苏东坡叹道：“______________________！”</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">后来，苏东坡为乱改菊花诗的事，专程向王安石“负荆请罪”，认错道歉。<a href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=51c26bd10102v7ah&amp;url=http://album.sina.com.cn/pic/001uPuOlzy6N7pviFG757\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"http://photo.blog.sina.com.cn/showpic.html#blogid=51c26bd10102v7ah&amp;url=http://album.sina.com.cn/pic/001uPuOlzy6N7pviFG757\"></a></p>","contentDesc":"","analysis":"","subContents":[{"content":"<p>选填恰当的词语。</p><p><span style=\"text-indent: 32px;\">苏东坡笑这两句诗是乱道，他认为一年四季，风各有名：春天为__$$__，夏天为__$$__，秋天为__$$__，冬天为__$$__。</span></p>","answers":[{"answer":"2","subAnswers":[],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null},{"answer":"3","subAnswers":[],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null},{"answer":"0","subAnswers":[],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null},{"answer":"1","subAnswers":[],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null}],"subContentTypeId":10,"analysis":"","optionType":"word","options":[{"option":"金风","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}},{"option":"朔风","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}},{"option":"和风","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}},{"option":"熏风","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}}],"hideOptionNumber":0,"listenUrl":"","listenName":"","listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"oralDict":{"seconds":null,"variables":null,"keywords":null,"options":null,"voiceText":null,"sentencePatterns":null,"picUrl":null,"picName":null,"beginListenUrl":null,"endListenUrl":null,"scorePercentage":null,"readySeconds":null,"listenFile":null,"contentDesc":null,"answers":null,"voiceTextsNew":null,"jsgf":null,"videoUrl":null,"videoCoverUrl":null,"highlightPos":null},"submitWays":[0],"tags":[101007],